  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下教育平台的数据流转链路。核心是学生数据库，然后成绩同步服务，再到LMS门户，最后到内容分发网络。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到您提到学生数据库作为起点，那GradeSync是负责把成绩数据推送到LMS吗？还有ContentCDN是承载课程资源的对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，GradeSync做成绩同步，LMS门户展示给学生看，CDN放视频课件。不过链路中间还有个环节——LMS查完数据后要回写一份到另一个学生库做归档。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那我画一个顺序流程：StudentDB → GradeSync → LMS_Portal → 另一个StudentDB → ContentCDN。这样五步，您看方向对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "方向是对的，但有两个StudentDB节点，得区分清楚。第一个是主库，第二个是归档库，虽然名字一样但功能不同。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出来，用a到e五个节点表示，主StudentDB是a，归档库是d，中间b是GradeSync，c是LMS_Portal，e是ContentCDN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "a",
        "b",
        "c",
        "d",
        "e"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚看了下，归档库那个节点标错了——我说的就是Education_StudentDB，但图上d的位置好像重复用了同样的标签，这没问题，但得确认d也是Education_StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "d",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：a是Education_StudentDB（主库），d也是Education_StudentDB（归档库），b是Education_GradeSync，c是Education_LMS_Portal，e是Education_ContentCDN。连接顺序是a连b，b连c，c连d，d连e。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "a",
        "b",
        "c",
        "d",
        "e",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是这个顺序。数据从主库出发，经过成绩同步，到门户展示，然后归档到另一个学生库，最后CDN提供内容下载。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，五个节点按TD纵向排列，a在最上，e在最下，四条连线形成完整链路。两个StudentDB虽然标签相同但在不同位置，符合您的设计。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "a",
        "b",
        "c",
        "d",
        "e"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "连线是单向的还是双向的？这里其实都是单向数据流，从上游到下游。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "a -- b",
        "b -- c",
        "c -- d",
        "d -- e"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "目前画的是无箭头连线，但表达的是顺序关系。需要改成带箭头的明确单向吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "a -- b",
        "b -- c",
        "c -- d",
        "d -- e"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "现在这样用双横线表示连接也可以，逻辑上是从a到e的流向，大家能理解就行。最终图就这样定稿吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "a",
        "b",
